English:
ERROR: No Log found with filename '{0}'

Usage: READ [FILENAME]

Attributes:
[FILENAME]     The name of the file to read

Example: READ myfile.txt, will output the contents of 'myfile.txt'

French.Translation:

Attributs :

Exemple : READ myfile.txt affichera le contenu de 'myfile.txt'.
